REMARK:
--#1 VW_ACK_LIS_SPCINFO

SELECT 

          j.bcno AS APARVL,

          j.regno AS CHTNO,

          CASE WHEN trim(j.sex) = 'F' THEN '2' ELSE '1' END AS ASEXID,

          j.age as AAGEVL,

          r1.rst AS ARETKD,

          NVL (R1.EGENERST, '0.00') AS EGENE,

          NVL (R1.ORF1AB, '0.00') AS ORF1AB,

          NVL (R1.RDRPRST, '0.00') AS RDRP,

          NVL (R1.N2GENERST, '0.00') AS NGENE,

          R1.GOODNM AS REANM,

          LIS.fn_ack_date_str(j.bcprtdt, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS AGETDT

     FROM LIS.lr010m r, LIS.lj010m j, LIS.lr0101m r1

    WHERE r.bcno = j.bcno 

        AND r.bcno = r1.bcno

        --리엔 파라미터

        AND (r.bcno = :검체번호 or r.bcno = fn_ack_get_bcno_normal(:검체번호))

;

 

--#2 VW_ACK_LIS_TESTINFO     

SELECT A.* FROM (        

SELECT DISTINCT

          j.bcno AS APARVL,

          j.regno AS CHTNO,

          CASE WHEN trim(j.sex) = 'F' THEN '2' ELSE '1' END AS ASEXID,

          j.age as AAGEVL,

          f.tnm AS TESTNAME,

          r.testcd AS TESTCODE,

          r.orgrst AS RESULT,

          R.HLMARK AS HLMARK,

          LIS.fn_ack_date_str(j.bcprtdt, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS AGETDT

     FROM LIS.lr010m r, LIS.lj010m j, LIS.lf060m f

    WHERE     r.bcno = j.bcno

          AND r.testcd = f.testcd

          AND r.spccd = f.spccd

          and r.tkdt >= f.usdt

          and r.tkdt < f.uedt

   UNION

   SELECT DISTINCT

          j.bcno AS APARVL,

          j.regno AS CHTNO,

          CASE WHEN trim(j.sex) = 'F' THEN '2' ELSE '1' END AS ASEXID,

          j.age as AAGEVL,

          f.tnm AS TESTNAME,

          r.testcd AS TESTCODE,

          r.orgrst AS RESULT,

          R.HLMARK AS HLMARK,

          LIS.fn_ack_date_str(j.bcprtdt, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS AGETDT

     FROM LIS.lm010m r, LIS.lj010m j, LIS.lf060m f

    WHERE     r.bcno = j.bcno

          AND r.testcd = f.testcd

          AND r.spccd = f.spccd

          and r.tkdt >= f.usdt

          and r.tkdt < f.uedt  

  ) A

  --리엔 파라미터

 WHERE A.APARVL = :검체번호

     AND A.TESTCODE IN (:검사코드)     

;
